descriptionHtml:
After the collapse of house Indoril and the eruption of Red Mountain, the houses\' secret of raising mudcrabs domestically was threatened to be lost forever! Fortunately, a lone familly of Mudcrab ranchers made it out of morrowind and migrated to skyrim, where their descendants still ply the time honored trade today.

This mod adds a Mudcrab Farm just north of Swindlers Den as well as a new ingredient; Mudcrab eggs!
author: Kyman3
